[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gwyn Jones: Scarlets flanker James Davies 'should go to the Olympic Games'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Gwyn Jones hopes Wales head coach Warren Gatland will "see the bigger picture" and encourage James Davies to take up a possible offer to play Rugby Sevens at this summer's Olympic Games.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
